<td valign="bottom" colspan="2"><br>
<font class="head">2001 International CES New Technology Pavilions</font>
<hr noshade size="1"></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2">

<table width="540" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
<tr><td>

<!-- content starts here --> 

<font class="body">
<a name="top"></a>
You have to be at the 2001 International CES to showcase your new technology products-the hottest consumer technology innovations.  Be part of the new technology pavilions, featuring up-to-the-minute trends in developing technologies.  Gain major exhibitor exposure at these highly-visible, heavy traffic, cost-effective pavilions.  
<ul>
<li><a href="#1394"><font class="body">1394 Showcase</font></a>
<li><a href="#bluetooth"><font class="body">Bluetooth*<sup>TM</sup> Pavilion</font></a>
<li><a href="#dsl"><font class="body">DSL Showcase</font></a>
<li><a href="#digitalcar"><font class="body">Digital Car Pavilion</font></a>
<li><a href="#digitalimg"><font class="body">Digital Imaging Pavilion</font></a>
<li><a href="#ecommerce"><font class="body">E-Commerce Pavilion</font></a>
<li><a href="#emerge"><font class="body">Emerging Technologies Pavilion</font></a>
<li><a href="#home"><font class="body">Home Security Pavilion</font></a> 
<li><a href="#databus"><font class="body">Intelligent Data Bus (IDB) Pavilion</font></a>
<!--- <li><a href="#irda"><font class="body">IrDA (Infrared Data Association) Pavilion</font></a> --->
<li><a href="#mp3"><font class="body">MP3 and Internet Audio</font></a>
<li><a href="#time"><font class="body">Timepiece Pavilion</font></a>
<li><a href="#upside"><font class="body"><i>Upside's</i> Digital Living Room Pavilion</font></a>
</ul>

For more information about exhibiting in a 2001 International CES New Technology Pavilion, <a href="/exhibitor/exhibit_info/contact.asp?menuItem=2&subMenuItem=1&tabName=Exhibitor">contact a CES Sales Representative</a>. <p>
<br clear="all">  
<hr width="100%" noshade><p>
<a name="1394"></a>
<img src="images/1394.jpg"><br><br>
<font class="subhead">1394 Showcase</a></font><br>
<i>Hosted by the 1394 Trade Association</i><br>
<i>Location: Las Vegas Convention Center (LVCC), South 1 &amp; 2</i><p>
Hot developments in 1394 technology provide near-universal connectivity and interoperability of digital video and audio devices.  Show attendees how 1394 applications will mold the future for everyone who makes, sells or uses consumer electronics. Demonstrate how 1394 technology is used to interconnect and control virtually any digital device, including DVD and CD players, digital converter boxes, DTVs, digital surround sound processors/receivers and personal video recorders. The 1394 Showcase promises to be one of the most heavily visited pavilions at the 2001 International CES.<p>

Join industry leaders like Apple, Kenwood, Panasonic, Texas Instruments and Sony who are pioneers with this innovative technology.<br>
<br>
<!--- <a href="javascript:submitForm()"><center><font size="1">get a list of exhibitors in this pavilion</font></center></a> --->
<a href="#top"><center><font size="1">back to the pavilion list</font></center></a><p>
<hr width="100%" noshade><p>
<a name="bluetooth"></a>
<img src="images/bluetooth.gif"><br><br>
<font class="subhead">Bluetooth*<sup>TM</sup> Pavilion</font><br>
<i>Endorsed by the Bluetooth*<sup>TM</sup> Special Interest Group</i><br>
<i>Location: LVCC, North 1 &amp; 2</i><p> 
Your role in the Bluetooth revolution enables two-way transmission of data, making efficient, fast, flawless, wireless connections a reality. With more than 1,300 manufacturers joining the Bluetooth family, Bluetooth technology is the fastest growing industry standard ever.  Be part of the Bluetooth Pavilion showcasing the best innovations using this cutting-edge digital technology.  Show us how to make wireless connections as simple as switching on the lights.<p> 
<i>*  Bluetooth is a trademark owned by its proprietor and used by CES under license.</i><br>
<br>
<!--- <a href="javascript:submitForm(4)"><center><font size="1">get a list of exhibitors in this pavilion</font></center></a> --->
<a href="#top"><center><font size="1">back to the pavilion list</font></center></a><p>
<hr width="100%" noshade><p>
<a name="dsl"></a>
<img src="images/dsl.gif"><br><br>
<font class="subhead">DSL Showcase</font><br>
<i>Hosted by the ADSL Forum</i><br>
<i>Location: LVCC, North 1 &amp; 2</i><p>
Twisted copper pairs may soon be obsolete.  Digital Subscriber Line (DSL) transforms ordinary phone lines into high-speed, digital lines for ultra-fast Internet access.  Your DSL innovations allow telecommuters access to corporate networks and enables interactive multimedia applications, and they want to learn more!  DSL is powering the future of the Internet, so be part of the 2001 International CES DSL Showcase.<br>
<br>
<!--- <a href="javascript:submitForm()"><center><font size="1">get a list of exhibitors in this pavilion</font></center></a> --->
<a href="#top"><center><font size="1">back to the pavilion list</font></center></a><p>
<hr width="100%" noshade><p>
<a name="digitalcar"></a>
<font class="subhead">Digital Car Pavilion</font><br>
<i>Location: Gold Pavilion</i><p>
Attendees want to experience the ride of the future at the Digital Car Pavilion.  Demonstrate the latest developments in vehicle navigation, global positioning systems (GPS), geographic information systems (GIS) satellites, vehicle safety, obstacle warning systems, emergency notification and wireless products.<p> 

Meet the partners you'll need to tap into the Digital Car marketplace.  Exhibit with other innovators, including ETL, InfoMove.com, Navigation Technologies, TravRoute and Ultradata Systems.<br>
<br>
<!--- <a href="javascript:submitForm(2)"><center><font size="1">get a list of exhibitors in this pavilion</font></center></a> --->
<a href="#top"><center><font size="1">back to the pavilion list</font></center></a><p>
<hr width="100%" noshade><p>
<a name="digitalimg"></a>
<font class="subhead">Digital Imaging Pavilion</font><br>
<i>Location: LVCC, North 1 &amp; 2</i><p>
Be part of the big picture in the Digital Imaging Pavilion at the 2001 International CES.
The digital market continues to explode as pixel counts increase and prices decrease, and you've got the power to make digital imaging easy, fun and affordable for all.<p>

Attendees want to see, feel, and test your digital cameras, flashcards, scanners and OCRs, software, monitors, printers, memory (film), batteries, cases and paper, not to mention video and electronic imaging and manipulation products, switchers, presentation equipment, imaging boards and training media.<p> 

Don't miss the exposure at the Digital Imaging Pavilion.  Join industry leaders such as Argus, Lexar, Media, Photo America and SMaL Camera.<br>
<br>
<!--- <a href="javascript:submitForm(3)"><center><font size="1">get a list of exhibitors in this pavilion</font></center></a> --->
<a href="#top"><center><font size="1">back to the pavilion list</font></center></a><p>
<hr width="100%" noshade><p>
<a name="ecommerce"></a>
<font class="subhead">E-Commerce Pavilion</font><br>
<i>Location:  LVCC, North 1 &amp; 2</i><p>
As dot-coms multiply, electronic commerce is soaring. Goods and services sold online increased 75 percent in 2000 over the previous year.  Attendees want you to show them how to sell more, streamline business operations and automate customer service, with your innovations at the E-Commerce Pavilion.<p>

Join pivotal players who make electronic commerce happen, including Advanced, Bidhit.com, 
E-Corporation, E-Sim, IMC, Shopguide and Tomax USA.<br>
<br>
<!--- <a href="javascript:submitForm(5)"><center><font size="1">get a list of exhibitors in this pavilion</font></center></a> --->
<a href="#top"><center><font size="1">back to the pavilion list</font></center></a><p>

<hr width="100%" noshade><p>
<a name="emerge"></a>
<font class="subhead">Emerging Technologies Pavilion</font><br> 
<i>Location: Silver Pavilion</i><p>
Display tomorrow's technologies today at the Emerging Technologies Pavilion, a showcase of the latest innovations in consumer technologies.  Everyone wants to be "up" on what's "in."  Financiers, investors, venture capitalists, retail buyers, the media, engineers and industry analysts flock to the Emerging Technologies Pavilion to see more than 30 growth companies and their next-generation products.  Don't miss being part of the most visited pavilion at CES!<br>
<br>
<!--- <a href="javascript:submitForm()"><center><font size="1">get a list of exhibitors in this pavilion</font></center></a> --->
<a href="#top"><center><font size="1">back to the pavilion list</font></center></a><p>
<hr width="100%" noshade><p>
<a name="home"></a>
<font class="subhead">Home Security Pavilion</font><br> 
<i>Location: LVCC, North 3 &amp; 4</i><p>
Home automation and security are among the fastest-growing product categories at the International CES.  You have the latest developments in integrated security systems, identification products, access control systems, intrusion detection devices, perimeter protection systems and closed- circuit TV.  Participate with other new companies in the Home Security Pavilion, and get your start at the International CES.<br>
<br>
<!--- <a href="javascript:submitForm(6)"><center><font size="1">get a list of exhibitors in this pavilion</font></center></a> --->
<a href="#top"><center><font size="1">back to the pavilion list</font></center></a><p>
<hr width="100%" noshade><p>
<a name="databus"></a>
<img src="images/idb.gif"><br><br>
<font class="subhead">Intelligent Data Bus (IDB) Pavilion</font><br>
<i>Sponsored by IDB Forum</i><br>
<i>Location: Gold Pavilion</i><p>
Intelligent Data Bus (IDB) plug-and-play technology enables consumers to buy and go.  Join the leading automobile manufacturers and other key companies of engineers who are eager to discuss the latest innovations in after market car products.<br>
<br>
<!--- <a href="javascript:submitForm()"><center><font size="1">get a list of exhibitors in this pavilion</font></center></a> --->
