<!--- 
<hr width="100%" noshade><p>
<a name="irda"></a>
<font class="subhead">IrDA (Infrared Data Association) Pavilion</font><br> 
<i>Location: TBD</i><p>
Infrared data applications are everywhere.  Join the excitement in the IrDA Pavilion, featuring consumer technologies that use new infrared data applications, including PDAs, printers, desktop adapters, notebooks, cameras and palm devices.  Share your expert knowledge on future infrared applications in copiers, fax machines, overhead projectors, telephones, bank ATMs, credit cards, game controls and headsets.  Be part of the news on breaking developments at the IrDA Pavilion.<p>
