<a name="upside"></a>
<img src="images/upside.gif">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src="images/dlrp.gif"><br><br>
<font class="subhead"><i>Upside's</i> Digital Living Room Pavilion</font><br>
<i>Sponsored by <i>Upside</i> Events</i><br>
<i>Location: Silver Pavilion</i><p>
Show us how to boost our lifestyle <i>and</i> workstyle in <i>Upside's</i> Digital Living Room Pavilion.  From digital televisions to voice-controlled thermostats, you hold the future of digital entertainment at your fingertips.  Attendees want to discover how to <i>truly</i> relax with digital innovations for the home market, and you have the solutions.<br>
<br>
